snippet.title: 10 Times Johnny Depp tried to WARN us ABOUT Amber Heard
snippet.description:
In the beginning everybody believed Amber Heard's accusations against Johnny Depp, however in this video we reveal 10 times Johnny Depp tried to warn us about Amber Heard.

Currently Amber Heard is under a ton of critique and is getting an enormous amount of hate due to her alleged lies on what really happened between her and her ex husband Johnny Depp.

Make sure to let us know what you think in the comments and subscribe to stay updated on everything happening in the celeb world. 

Stay safe, much love!
